These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Color: azure, light-blue
Cigar: davidoff, bluemaster
1. Cigar:davidoff is in an even position##4
2. Cigar:bluemaster == Color:light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Color   | light-blue | azure |
| Cigar     | bluemaster    | davidoff   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Flower: poppy, lily
Food: cauliflower, mango
1. Food:cauliflower is in an odd position##4
2. Flower:lily is on the left of Flower:poppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Flower   | lily | poppy        |
| Food      | cauliflower  | mango |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
House: victorian, futuristic
Game: backgammon, canasta
1. Game:backgammon is in an odd position##4
2. House:futuristic is on the left of House:victorian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| House   | futuristic    | victorian |
| Game   | backgammon | canasta |

